Yes, you can use it multiple times. You just have to set it for the next IRQ inside each IRQ. Though I think there is a minimum 2-scanline limit, so you can't have interrupts every scanline.<p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://forums.nesdev.com/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=95">tokumaru</a> — Tue Sep 19, 2006 10:16 am</p><hr />
